data.description: Turnkey Newburgh Hts duplex, fully-rented (down $900, up $826). Separately metered gas & electric. Many updates including vinyl/aluminum siding, new kitchen cabinets in '24 downstairs, upgraded electric panels, newer hot water tanks, 1 newer furnace. Each unit is 2 beds, 1 bath. Other features: basement laundry facilities, driveway for plenty of off-street parking, spacious front porch, ceiling fans, walk-up attic for storage or potential additional living space (1-2 bedrooms). Convenient location near freeway access, shopping, schools, just minutes to Downtown Cleveland, Airport, University Circle, Amazon, and Cleveland Clinic.
